</div>
<div style="column-count:3;-moz-column-count:3;-webkit-column-count:3">
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Clash_of_Civilizations" title="Clash of Civilizations" class="mw-redirect">Clash of Civilizations</a></li>
